Program: Outlook
Title: Fleeing from Violence in Burundi
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrb2
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The story of one boy fleeing violence in Burundi by stowing on a ship for St Helena. Also, a journey to the Amazon with artists Olly and Suzi who encourage poisonous tarantula spiders onto their canvases. And, celebrating St Patrick's Day in Moscow.